# Implementation Plan - Phase 3: Visual Updates & Cleanup

## Goal
Enhance user experience with visual updates, implement requested UI changes (Swipe to Save), and ensure code cleanliness by removing legacy dependencies.

## Completed Changes
- **FaceID**: Implemented and Verified.
- **UI Updates**:
    - [x] **Swipe to Save**: Replaced standard button with [SwipeToSaveWidget](file:///Users/aniruddhmodi/Documents/Aniruddh/Extracurricular/flutter-app/the_30sec_journal/lib/widgets/swipe_to_save_widget.dart#5-18).
    - [x] **Microphone Alignment**: Fixed overlap in [TodayScreen](file:///Users/aniruddhmodi/Documents/Aniruddh/Extracurricular/flutter-app/the_30sec_journal/lib/screens/today_screen.dart#17-25).
    - [x] **Star Button**: Restored accidentally removed button.
- **Code Cleanup**:
    - [x] **Firebase Removal**: Removed `Firebase.initializeApp`, `Firestore` usage in [FeedbackScreen](file:///Users/aniruddhmodi/Documents/Aniruddh/Extracurricular/flutter-app/the_30sec_journal/lib/screens/feedback_screen.dart#6-13), and deleted [firestore_service.dart](file:///Users/aniruddhmodi/Documents/Aniruddh/Extracurricular/flutter-app/the_30sec_journal/lib/screens/firestore_service.dart).
    - [x] **Settings Fix**: Updated [SettingsScreen](file:///Users/aniruddhmodi/Documents/Aniruddh/Extracurricular/flutter-app/the_30sec_journal/lib/screens/settings_screen.dart#18-25) to use [AuthService](file:///Users/aniruddhmodi/Documents/Aniruddh/Extracurricular/flutter-app/the_30sec_journal/lib/services/auth_service.dart#4-40) instead of `FirebaseAuth`.

- **Functional Changes**:
    - [x] **Microphone Toggle**: Changed from hold-to-record to tap-to-toggle.
    - [x] **Email Feedback**: Feedback now launches email with pre-filled content.

